"{\"uid\": \"aljazeera.com-news-2024-10-17-former-canadian-olympian-charged-in-major-us-cocaine-smuggling-case\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Snowboarder Ryan Wedding and 15 others are accused of shipping 60 tonnes of cocaine a year to the US and Canada.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snowboarding\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snowboarder\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snowboarding\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snowboarding\"}, {\"begin\": 12, \"end\": 16, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9791380657834444, \"rank\": 0.015797952670247657, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"score\": 0.91757728752024, \"rank\": 0.07742750577304489, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\"}, {\"begin\": 105, \"end\": 111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999981228742737, \"rank\": 1.7342027623027992e-06, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Save  Share  United States prosecutors in Los Angeles, California, have charged a former Olympic snowboarder with allegedly running a large and violent cocaine smuggling operation out of Mexico.\", \"from\": 114, \"to\": 308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 127, \"end\": 140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.5519190995734816, \"rank\": 0.8118597467866729, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 169, \"end\": 179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.9999999917026798, \"rank\": 8.106490886968966e-09, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}, {\"begin\": 301, \"end\": 307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9947629275965134, \"rank\": 0.005264593780579945, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Thursday, the Department of Justice unveiled a 52-page indictment accusing the 43-year-old Canadian athlete, Ryan James Wedding, and 15 other people, of shipping 60 tonnes of cocaine a year from Colombia to Canada and the US using long-haul semi-trucks.\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 404, \"end\": 412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.988984661202758, \"rank\": 0.011138015284463275, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 422, \"end\": 432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_James_(rugby_league)\", \"score\": 0.9858044152224581, \"rank\": 0.014399999999998954, \"text\": \"Ryan James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_James_(rugby_league)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_James_(rugby_league)\"}, {\"begin\": 508, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999872671, \"rank\": 1.1299447479502203e-11, \"text\": \"Colombia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia\"}, {\"begin\": 520, \"end\": 526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999981228742737, \"rank\": 1.7342027623027992e-06, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 535, \"end\": 537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"score\": 0.91757728752024, \"rank\": 0.07742750577304489, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The FBI is offering a $50,000 reward for information leading to the arrest and extradition of Wedding, who is considered a fugitive and uses the aliases El Jefe, Giant and Public Enemy.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Bureau_of_Investigation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.937683672111258e-48, \"text\": \"FBI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Bureau_of_Investigation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Bureau_of_Investigation\"}, {\"begin\": 721, \"end\": 728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/El_Jefe_(jaguar)\", \"score\": 0.9999999016831729, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"El Jefe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/El_Jefe_(jaguar)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/El_Jefe_(jaguar)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Agents also raided a $5m luxury mansion near Miami in South Florida and arrested its owner, 36-year-old music executive and restaurant owner Nahim Jorge Bonilla, who was also named in the indictment, The Miami Herald reported.\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 800, \"end\": 805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami\", \"score\": 0.9999993954913415, \"rank\": 6.038757817958438e-07, \"text\": \"Miami\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami\"}, {\"begin\": 809, \"end\": 822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Florida\", \"score\": 0.9999998249986828, \"rank\": 1.6588901414986242e-07, \"text\": \"South Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Florida\"}, {\"begin\": 955, \"end\": 971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami_Herald\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Miami Herald\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami_Herald\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami_Herald\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bonilla allegedly received 12 kilogrammes (about 44lbs) of cocaine from Wedding and his co-defendant Andrew Clark to distribute.\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the indictment, Bonilla was in debt to Clark and Wedding, and the two men threatened to kill Bonilla's mother if he did not repay what was owed.\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1269, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wedding, who competed in the 2002 Winter Olympics in Salt Lake City, also faces charges in Canada in a separate drug case.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1324, \"end\": 1338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"score\": 0.9971377936493744, \"rank\": 0.002870422033912401, \"text\": \"Salt Lake City\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\"}, {\"begin\": 1362, \"end\": 1368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999981228742737, \"rank\": 1.7342027623027992e-06, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was previously convicted in the US of conspiracy to distribute cocaine and was sentenced to prison in 2010, federal records show.\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1429, \"end\": 1431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"score\": 0.91757728752024, \"rank\": 0.07742750577304489, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"US authorities believe that, after Wedding's release, he resumed drug trafficking for the notoriousSinaloa Cartel in Mexico.\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1528, \"end\": 1530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"score\": 0.91757728752024, \"rank\": 0.07742750577304489, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\"}, {\"begin\": 1645, \"end\": 1651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9947629275965134, \"rank\": 0.005264593780579945, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He chose to become a major drug trafficker, and he chose to become a killer,\\\" Martin Estrada, the US attorney in Los Angeles, told reporters on Thursday.\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1733, \"end\": 1739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\", \"score\": 0.9426681817129147, \"rank\": 0.06081865168950102, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 1740, \"end\": 1747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_Estrada\", \"score\": 0.999993718343324, \"rank\": 6.254481599931911e-06, \"text\": \"Estrada\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_Estrada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_Estrada\"}, {\"begin\": 1753, \"end\": 1764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Attorney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"US attorney\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Attorney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Attorney\"}, {\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9794628761950264, \"rank\": 0.020967664597430293, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Authorities also explained that they seized cocaine, weapons, ammunition, cash and more than $3m in cryptocurrency in connection to their investigation.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1962, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Wedding, the Olympian snowboarder, went from navigating slopes to contouring a life of incessant crimes,\\\" said Matthew Allen, the special agent in charge of the Drug Enforcement Administration (DEA) in Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 2179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2084, \"end\": 2089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\", \"score\": 0.7854438519099015, \"rank\": 0.2689321066366341, \"text\": \"Allen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\"}, {\"begin\": 2126, \"end\": 2163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource