 6.892748288645556e-06, \"text\": \"Ontario\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario\"}, {\"begin\": 2528, \"end\": 2534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999981228742737, \"rank\": 1.7342027623027992e-06, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At least one other person was also killed by the group.\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wedding's co-defendant Clark, 34, is also a Canadian citizen.\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2697, \"end\": 2713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_nationality_law\", \"score\": 0.9999906179126735, \"rank\": 9.382175455436939e-06, \"text\": \"Canadian citizen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_nationality_law\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_nationality_law\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Known by the alias \\\"The Dictator\\\", he was arrested by Mexican authorities on October 8, according to the Justice Department.\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2769, \"end\": 2776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexicans\", \"score\": 0.9975386961056281, \"rank\": 0.002467341542880732, \"text\": \"Mexican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexicans\"}, {\"begin\": 2820, \"end\": 2838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Justice\", \"score\": 0.9999999999561169, \"rank\": 4.392007011950473e-11, \"text\": \"Justice Department\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Justice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Just